<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Hare_Krishna&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Non Hare Krishna organizations">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Non Hare Krishna organizations</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.sivanandadlshq.org/teachings/sankirtanyoga.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.sivanandadlshq.org/teachings/sankirtanyoga.htm" rel="nofollow">" Pujya Sivananda Maharaj - Divine Life Society</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YWs5iNIj5DY" class="external text" title="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YWs5iNIj5DY" rel="nofollow">"Hare Rama Hare Krishna" kirtan with Jagadguru Kripalu Ji Maharaj</a></li>
<li><a href="http://shree-kripaluji-maharaj.blogspot.com/2009/01/important-hare-ram-sankirtan.html" class="external text" title="http://shree-kripaluji-maharaj.blogspot.com/2009/01/important-hare-ram-sankirtan.html" rel="nofollow">Maha Mantra Sung in 6 Different Melodies</a></li>
</ul>
